result.name: Sushi Hanami

reviews.text: All the seafood were really fresh and the size of the sushi rice were just right. The freshness of the sushi just melt into your mouth. And the chef will explain to you the name and the characteristics of each piece of sushi. And even though the restaurant was full, their service was simply perfect. Will surely drop by again in the very near future.
Serves very good sushi that doesn't taste fishy at all. Serves a wide range of sushi, as well. I recommend ordering the "Kanpachi (Greater Amberjack)" raw or seared.
I've been to sushi places all over the world and this might have been the best one yet. Well priced for the outstanding quality.
Good lunch with great quality and variety of sushi. Will be back for dinner.
Good sake selection.  Food is decent
